<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>License Expiry Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffc107;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffc107;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .expiry-warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .license-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .days-remaining {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ö†Ô∏è License Expiry Notice</h1>
            <p>Hello {{userName}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-warning">
            <h3>Your License is Expiring Soon</h3>
            <p class="days-remaining">{{daysUntilExpiry}} days remaining</p>
        </div>

        <div class="license-info">
            <p><strong>License Key:</strong> {{licenseKey}}</p>
            <p><strong>Days Until Expiry:</strong> {{daysUntilExpiry}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>To ensure uninterrupted access to your applications, please contact our support team to renew your license
            before it expires.</p>

        <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
            <h4>üÜò Contact Support</h4>
            <p>For license renewal or assistance:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2025 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>